Package net.okocraft.box.api.transaction

Class InventoryTransaction

java.lang.Object
net.okocraft.box.api.transaction.InventoryTransaction
@Deprecated(since="5.5.0", forRemoval=true) @ScheduledForRemoval(inVersion="6.0.0") public final class InventoryTransaction extends Object
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
use StockHolderTransaction or InventoryUtil
A class for transacting with inventory.

All methods of this class must be called in the server main thread.
